result.formatted_address: 40B San Tsuen St, Tsuen Wan, Hong Kong
result.name: Gala Cafe

reviews.text: Dont expect too much from a old fashion restaurant in HK. The egg sandwich are amazing must try item. The omelette with Beef is also good. the Price for food is reasonable but for drinks its a Joke.
Excellent brunch!  Some of the best chicken wings I've had. Local spot but sometimes you might have to wait for a table. And yes you must try the Ovaltine drinks.

First of all,  if u haven't been there and wanting to,  forget about it.

Food quality is fairly ok but there is really nothing special otherwise.

The milk tea 茶走 I had was overly sweetened by a lot, a novice mistake. 

In terms of decoration,  there are plenty of cha chaan teng in Hong Kong which are similar, and indeed many more are more so called "nostalgic".

Hygiene-wise,  I just cannot stand the surgical gloves all the staff members wear,  they wear it to do everything.

And the so called famous thick sandwiches and hefty portion of food,  forgive me I would never understand or appreciate why making things big make the food better.

And this I have to say in Cantonese ,  呢間野茶餐快餐早餐下午茶餐都無 跟本唔可以叫冰廳！

Don't waste your time waiting here,  there are plenty of annonymous cha chaan teng or 冰廳 in Hong Kong waiting for you to discover.9

Delicious and fulfilling sandwich, with huge egg omelette and beef as filler.
The price is cheap, good for breakfast or brunch.
Also serve another menu like noodles and fried chicken.
Also the ovaltine is really good also.

Waited for 45 mins to get in to the restaurant (expected), then waited for another 45 mins to get my food (unexpected). Omelet is way to salty and watery. Those bread on top of the omelet are sliced unevenly and horribly ugly (see attached photos for proof). Only one staff was paying efforts to take care of the customers and all others are just wandering and daydreaming. Drinks are too sweet. Although I did expect the quality will drop a bit after the original boss selling this restaurant to some inexperienced guy, I didn't expect such a terrible dining experience. If the new boss dont give a fxxk on this matter, they should probably close it asap for god sake. I will only recommend this restaurant to someone I hate.

result.adr_address: 香港荃灣新村街40B號
result.name: 嘉樂冰廳

reviews.text:
一個星期四的下午三時前後去到，不用排隊，稍等後，有搭枱位，可以嘆下。 姐姐仔招呼得快，亦留意食客需要。

三文治足料，鮮牛同蛋都豐富。配合奶茶的整體味道舒服。 祇是覺得有少少偏貴😉。
超多遊客，如果是想去旅遊景點就去啱左！叫左牛肉意（等候時間35分鐘），奄列（等候時間15分鐘），凍央（等候時間10分鐘）意粉好大碗！中式味道？！好淡口！奄列好大碟，蛋還蛋，腿還腿，熟蛋係上面，半生係碟底，火腿微暖。凍央幾好味。全部食物就煮到唔似冰室樣....人冇禮貌，野食冇套餐，味道非常一般。餓起上黎唔洗錢係我前面可能會再食，要排隊俾錢，no way la
轉左老細後啲嘢吾好食，以前的蛋又滑又有蛋味，而家老到死，一星都吾想比

香港懷舊冰室-嘉樂冰廳

試了招牌的火腿小奄列
大大份一點都不小😂
蛋量很多很厚，火腿也比一般茶餐廳的好吃

牛肉米粉 牛肉很多，調味比較重手
份量也超多，一個女生吃不完😂

叉燒麵一般，用來填飽肚子的😅

飲品還好😂
